@URL_API = http://localhost:3000

### GET all languages
GET {{URL_API}}/languages
Content-Type: application/json

### GET all Options
GET {{URL_API}}/options
Content-Type: application/json

#### Serie ENDPOINTS

### CREATE Serie
POST {{URL_API}}/series
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute!",
